e" style=""><div class="x-feature-box-graphic-inner square" style="font-size: 175px;"><img class="square" src="http://navcoin.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Artboard-7-copy-5-1.png" style="margin: 0 auto;"></div></div></div><div class="x-feature-box-content"><h4 class="x-feature-box-title">Earn While You Sleep</h4><p class="x-feature-box-text">With Proof of Stake, you can earn up to 5% interest on your investment simply by switching your wallet to staking mode.</p></div></div><hr class="x-gap" style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;"></div><div class="x-column x-sm x-1-3" style="padding: 0px 0px 20px; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px); transition-duration: 750ms;" data-x-element="column" data-x-params="{&quot;fade&quot;:true}" data-fade="true"><div class="x-feature-box center-text top-text cf" style="color: #fff;font-size:16px; max-width: none;" data-x-element="feature_box" data-x-params="{&quot;child&quot;:false,&quot;graphicAnimation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;graphicAnimationOffset&quot;:&quot;50&quot;,&quot;graphicAnimationDelay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}"><div class="x-feature-box-graphic square"><div class="x-feature-box-graphic-outer square" style=""><div class="x-feature-box-graphic-inner square" style="font-size: 175px;"><img class="square" src="http://navcoin.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Artboard-7-copy-6-2.png" style="margin: 0 auto;"></div></div></div><div class="x-feature-box-content"><h4 class="x-feature-box-title">Optional Private Payments</h4><p class="x-feature-box-text">Send encrypted private transactions through our dual blockchain powered NAVTech system.</p></div></div><hr class="x-gap" style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;"></div></div></div><div id="x-section-5" class="x-section cs-ta-center" style="margin: 0px;padding: 65px 0px; background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 96%);"><div class="x-container max width" style="margin: 0px auto;padding: 0px;"><div class="x-column x-sm x-1-2" style="padding: 0 0px;"><hr class="x-gap" style="margin: 60px 0 0 0;"><img class="x-img x-img-none" src="http://navcoin.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Artboard-2-2.png" alt="Nav Coin Core Wallet"><hr class="x-gap" style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;"></div><div class="x-column x-sm x-1-2" style="padding: 0px; opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px); transition-duration: 750ms;" data-x-element="column" data-x-params="{&quot;fade&quot;:true}" data-fade="true"><h2 class="h-custom-headline h3"><span>It’s Easy to Use</span></h2><hr class="x-gap" style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;"><div class="x-text" style="font-size:16px;"><p>The Nav Coin wallet has been carefully refined to be intuitive and easy to use. It comes with a setup wizard and everything you need to load the blockchain and start sending transactions in a secure environment.</p>
<p>Making a private payment is simple and the coins arrive at their destination in minutes. Just tick the box and send the coins, NAVTech handles the rest. </p>
